content: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <rdf:RDF xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/" xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#"> <channel rdf:about="http://hdl.handle.net/10283/617"> <title>An N-body simulation of M4</title> <link>http://hdl.handle.net/10283/617</link> <description>This repository contains datasets from a large N-body simulation of the globular cluster M4.  Snapshots giving a full list of data for all particles (mass, position, velocity, stellar type, stellar radius, V magnitude, B-V colour) are given at almost 400 instants in the lifetime of the model.  The simulation is described in the paper "Towards an N-body model of the globular cluster M4", submitted to MNRAS.</description> <items> <rdf:Seq> <rdf:li rdf:resource="http://hdl.handle.net/10283/618"/> </rdf:Seq> </items> <dc:date>2015-03-19T23:01:26Z</dc:date> </channel> <item rdf:about="http://hdl.handle.net/10283/618"> <title>Snapshots of an N-body model of M4</title> <link>http://hdl.handle.net/10283/618</link> <description>Snapshots of an N-body model of M4 326 snapshots of an N-body model of the Galactic globular cluster M4.  Each snapshot consists of a list of all the particles in the simulation at one time. </description> <dc:date>2014-09-04T09:28:57Z</dc:date> </item> </rdf:RDF>
